###  https://w3id.org/tabulae/id/codes/anclass/ETSCover
<https://w3id.org/tabulae/id/codes/anclass/ETSCover> rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                                                              <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#Concept> ,
                                                              :AnnotationClass ;
